query:
SELECT
                d.identity as "identity: String",
                CASE WHEN count(*) > 3 THEN AVG(reliability) ELSE 100 END as "value: f32"
            FROM
                gateway_details d
            JOIN
                gateway_status s on d.id = s.gateway_details_id
            WHERE
                timestamp >= ? AND
                timestamp <= ?
            GROUP BY 1
